      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>The ossuary is worn; the lid, flat with fingergrips, is broken. Second word of the inscription is on the chest's front; third is on the back side. The first word, possibly effaced traces of an earlier inscription, is just above the second, on the chest's front. Its reading is highly speculative.</p>
         </div>
